content: App doesn't work. When you sign in it just closed the app
This new update for March 2016 is better. No more loading frame by frame.  Faster loading.  Thank You.  But the Wi-Fi still won't connect.
Doesn't work playback not very good

Great App, OK customer support, but, as soon as they came out with this addition the push config, that is the part that sends you a text message when a camera senses motion, stopped working. Tech support says there is nothing they can do. That was one of the main futures I bought the system for.
I love that I can show more than 4 feeds at a time and that I can search videos. Good job!
